# This project has no runtime environment variables.
# All configuration lives inside Code.js constants and appsscript.json.
#
# The one value you must update before deploying to a new domain is:
#
#   DEFAULT_SPREADSHEET_URL (Code.js, line 1)
#
# This is a hard-coded fallback sheet URL used when a new user
# has not yet saved their own default spreadsheet preference.
# Replace it with a Sheet URL that is shared with all users on your domain.
#
# Example:
#   DEFAULT_SPREADSHEET_URL = "https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/YOUR_SHEET_ID/edit"
#
# ---
#
# For local clasp authentication, clasp stores credentials in:
#   ~/.clasprc.json   (global login)
#   .clasprc.json     (project-level login, gitignored)
#
# Never commit .clasprc.json. It contains OAuth refresh tokens.
